    <li>colonistCountToLend(colonistsToLendCount==1)->1 colonist[minAgeOrOlder]</li>
    <li>colonistCountToLend(colonistsToLendCount>1)->[colonistsToLendCount] colonists[minAgeOrOlder]</li>
    <li>willSendShuttle->[asker_pronoun] will send a shuttle to pick up the [colonists].</li>
    <li>colonists(colonistsToLendCount==1)->colonist</li>
    <li>colonists(colonistsToLendCount>1)->colonists</li>
    <li>minAgeOrOlder(minAge==0)-></li>
    <li>minAgeOrOlder(minAge>0)-> [minAge] years old or older</li>
    <li>pawnListHaveConjugation(colonistsToLendCount==1)->has</li>
    <li>pawnListHaveConjugation(colonistsToLendCount>1)->have</li>
  -->
  <PawnLend.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription(asker_factionLeader==True)->[asker_faction_leaderTitle] [asker_nameFull] trong số [asker_faction_name] cần thêm sự giúp đỡ của [dutyDescription].\n\n[asker_pronoun] đang nhờ bạn cho vay [asker_objective] [colonistCountToLend] trong [lendForDays] ngày.\n\n[willSendShuttle]</li>
    <li>disease->cúm</li>
    <li>disease->bệnh dịch hạch</li>
    <li>disease->bệnh sốt rét</li>
    <li>disease->sự nhiễm trùng</li>
    <li>questDescription(asker_royalInCurrentFaction==True)->[asker_royalTitleInCurrentFaction] [asker_nameFull] trong số [asker_faction_name] cần mọi người giúp đỡ [dutyRoyalDescription].\n\n[asker_pronoun] đang nhờ bạn cho vay [colonistCountToLend] để phục vụ [asker_objective] trong [lendForDays] ngày.\n\n[willSendShuttle]</li>
    <li>colonistCountToLend(colonistsToLendCount==1)->1 cư dân[minAgeOrOlder]</li>
    <li>colonistCountToLend(colonistsToLendCount>1)->[colonistsToLendCount] cư dân[minAgeOrOlder]</li>
    <li>willSendShuttle->[asker_pronoun] sẽ cử xe đưa đón đến đón [colonists].</li>
    <li>colonists(colonistsToLendCount==1)->cư dân</li>
    <li>colonists(colonistsToLendCount>1)->cư dân</li>
    <li>minAgeOrOlder(minAge==0)-></li>
    <li>minAgeOrOlder(minAge>0)->[minAge] tuổi trở lên</li>
    <li>pawnListHaveConjugation(colonistsToLendCount==1)->có</li>
    <li>pawnListHaveConjugation(colonistsToLendCount>1)->có</li>
  </PawnLend.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
